      "role": "user",
      "content": "The moon feels too heavy tonight, almost like it's pressing the very breath from my lungs. Everything is gone... the promises, the warmth, the light. It feels as though I am merely a ghost haunting my own life, waiting for the shadows to finally claim what is left of me. There is no solace in the dawn, only the exhaustion of continuing a story that has already reached its tragic end.",
